    <stitle>10 SPEED TRANSMISSIONS EATON RTLO SERIES - REMOVE - COUNTERSHAFT ASSEMBLIES</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="remove" graphiccount="1">
        <title>COUNTERSHAFT ASSEMBLIES</title>
        <para>Except for the PTO gears, the upper and lower countershaft assemblies are the same. Make sure to mark each
            as they are removed.
        </para>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Move the upper countershaft assembly to the rear as far as possible.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Swing the countershaft front to the middle of the case.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Lift the countershaft assembly from the case (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1301747">Figure 47</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f1301747" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g1301747" filename="../figg13/G1301747.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 47. Countershaft Assembly From Case</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
    </svcproc>
